 {"id":"br-r37-c1-kilv4","title":"test_stochastic_block_model_default_uses_native_fast_path asserts wrong contract since br-sbmrng","description":"Pre-existing failure in test_sbm_generators.py::test_stochastic_block_model_default_uses_native_fast_path: asserts that fnx.stochastic_block_model calls _rust_stochastic_block_model (the native Rust fast path).

